title: Private Patio or Balcony Space (select homes), Cards & Crafts Room
posting_body: ['At The Legends of Champlin Senior Apartments, our residents enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location.', 'Our one, two and three bedroom apartment homes have unbeatable amenities with in-home washers and dryers, granite countertops, spacious 9-foot ceilings, and a private balcony or patio.', 'With our convenient location off highway 169 – just steps from Elm Creek Park Preserve which features beautiful lakes, picnic areas, and walking/biking trails there is no better place than The Legends to call your new home!', 'Hurry and reserve your new home today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Kitchen Breakfast Bar or Island', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Additional Storage Available', '- Large Walk-In Closet(s)', '- Community Library & Business Center', '- Guest Suite Available', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Champlin is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Champlin', '11635 Theatre Drive', 'Champlin, MN, 55316', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'wABjxq7W1H1']
